# Per-Dockerfile ignore (ADR-0014). BuildKit uses <Dockerfile>.dockerignore in
# preference to the repo-root .dockerignore — which is tuned for the Go service
# images and excludes apps/, libs/ts, and package.json, all of which the frontend
# build needs. Here we exclude only VCS/dep/build-output dirs and the unrelated
# admin app, keeping the context correct for `bun run build`.
**/.git
**/.DS_Store
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.turbo
apps/admin
